targets.expr:
sum (
  min_over_time(
    up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_select"}[$__rate_interval]
  )
  unless on(instance)
  up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_insert"}
)

sum (
  min_over_time(
    up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_insert"}[$__rate_interval]
  )
  unless on(instance)
  up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_select"}
)

sum(
  min_over_time(
    up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_select"}[$__rate_interval]
  )
  and on(instance)
  up{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance_insert"}
)

panels.description:
Shows how many log entries were ignored or dropped on insertion due to various reasons:
* timestamp out of retention period or timestamp in future;
* number of fields per entry exceeded.
